        <updateDate>2005-09-12T14:07:32Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Authorizes the superintendent of a military service academy to have in effect a policy of offering a voluntary, nondenominational prayer at an authorized academy activity, subject to such limitations as the Secretary of Defense may prescribe.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
